(47756, 72723, 4390, 11, 'Rock Your Body －Steve Good- Jobs', '作詞人STEVE GOOD-JOB 的臉書連結: http://www.facebook.com/Lbiza?ref=ts#!/Lbiza/info\r\n作曲人Patricia Shih 的臉書連結：http://www.facebook.com/Lbiza?ref=ts#!/patriciashih457/info\r\n', '2012-06-10 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, '<Rock your Body>\r\n詞：Steve Good-Jobs 2012/2/19 \r\n曲+ 唱：Patricia Shih 2012/02/27\r\n\r\n曲序: A1-->A2-->C-->A1-->A2-->C-->D-->C\r\n\r\nA1\r\n吃喔吃喔 拎喔拎喔\r\n蟹蝦魚肉配啤酒\r\n我的壓力憂愁成為吃到飽的藉口\r\nA2\r\n不要不要 come on come on\r\n口裡雖然說不要\r\n嘴巴卻誠實的張開 迎接食物們來到\r\nB\r\n切掉腦袋的索求 給我安靜幾秒鐘\r\n讓搖滾樂降臨 拯救直線上升的體重\r\nC\r\nrock your body rock your body\r\n抖一抖身上老愛回鍋的肉\r\nrock your body rock your body\r\n呼喚沉睡已久呆滯的脈搏\r\nrock your body everybody\r\n體驗久違的輕盈跳上月球\r\nrock your body everybody\r\n奔馳汗水後 (那)痛快的笑容 \r\nD\r\n面對鏡子前那個全新的自我\r\n點點頭 不再自我墮落 答應我 要乖乖運動\r\n點點頭 不再大魚大肉 相信我 每天 rock n roll', '', 237, '', 'Patricia Shih ', 'Steve Good-Jobs', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-18 17:49:44', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47757, 58111, 0, 1, '我不知道', '這個社會怎麼了？\r\n還是我自己怎麼了？\r\n我不知道\r\n\r\n------------------------------------\r\n主唱：江國銘\r\n吉他：江國銘\r\n貝斯：江國銘\r\n鼓　：江國銘\r\n編曲：江國銘\r\n混音：江國銘\r\n錄製：江國銘\r\n------------------------------------', '2012-05-18 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 2, 4, '214　我不知道　201109282213\r\n\r\n站在熟悉的街道問自己\r\n為什麼存在　我不知道　我不知道\r\n回到家面對網路世界的自己\r\n那個是誰　我不知道　我不知道\r\n\r\noh~oh~　為什麼存在　我不知道　還有誰知道\r\noh~oh~　那個是誰　我不知道　還有誰知道\r\n\r\n夢想什麼時候開始墜落　朋友怎麼一個又變了一個\r\n愛情什麼時候開始墮落　現實怎麼越來越真實了\r\n\r\n每天的生活成為了規律\r\n有什麼意義　我不知道　我不知道\r\n時間偷偷改變鏡子中的自己\r\n變成了誰　我不知道　我不知道\r\n\r\noh~oh~　有什麼意義　我不知道　還有誰知道\r\noh~oh~　變成了誰　我不知道　還有誰知道\r\n\r\n夢想什麼時候開始墜落　朋友怎麼一個又變了一個\r\n愛情什麼時候開始墮落　現實怎麼越來越真實了\r\n\r\n我不知道他不知道你不知道　究竟還有誰能知道\r\n你知道嗎　你了解嗎\r\n我不知道他不知道你不知道　究竟還有誰能知道\r\n我不知道　我不知道\r\n', '', 243, '', '江國銘', '江國銘', '江國銘', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-18 21:58:46', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47758, 129787, 0, 1, '小小的希望', '三個禮拜前\r\n工作到一半的我\r\n接到了親人的電話\r\n說我媽媽肺癌偷偷去住院了...\r\n我真的崩潰了....', '2012-05-19 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, '小小的希望\r\n\r\n詞曲編曲製作 / Yawi\r\n\r\n媽媽 請妳別擔心\r\n有我在身邊\r\n牽著妳的手  為妳禱告\r\n\r\n主阿  我全然相信\r\n相信祢恩典\r\n賜與我媽媽 無比的力量\r\n\r\n主  請祢垂聽呼求\r\n我的禱告\r\n我一點小小的希望\r\n\r\n媽媽妳不需要太擔心\r\n妳一定會一天一天健康\r\n只要妳相信耶穌 祂的恩典\r\n必讓妳康復\r\n因為我們都是神的孩子\r\n\r\n相信祂的恩典  必讓妳康復\r\n', '', 233, '', 'Yawi', 'Yawi', 'Yawi', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-05-19 00:03:05', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47759, 36760, 0, 1, '乾淨的土地 Demo', '生活在城市裡   \r\n\r\n我們的環境被受汙染  \r\n\r\n我們的心靈也同時的遭受破壞 \r\n                      \r\n所以請給我們自已 一個乾淨的土地 ', '2012-05-19 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 2, 7, '乾淨的土地  (台語)\r\n\r\n主歌\r\n希望  我身邊 \r\n有你的笑容的春天\r\n陪伴我每一個過去\r\n陪伴我每一個過去\r\n \r\n別作夢 就走出去\r\n有什麼 沒辦法的事情\r\n一步一步 一腳印\r\n一步一步 一腳印\r\n \r\n你是否有看過  ((失去了這個世界沒勇氣 \r\n沒面容的臉\r\n到底是什麼原因\r\n變的這麼沒人情\r\n \r\nPre-Chorus\r\n這條路  轉不出去\r\n我的心  放不下去\r\n別再說  聽不下去\r\n現在讓我出去\r\n \r\n副歌\r\n給我一個 乾淨的土地\r\n別再黑白講 我想要簡單的過', '', 235, '', 'CastAway', 'CastAway', '', '', '', 1, 0, 1, '2012-05-19 00:41:59', '2013-10-07 17:21:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47760, 148203, 0, 1, 'Thoughts of Dying Liberal (Demo)', '', '2009-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'There are many white squares\r\nfilling up my field of view\r\nNo windows, no outside breathing air\r\nWith water, and some chromatic pills\r\n\r\nAll the white squares start spinning in\r\ndirection against the globe\r\nI’m going to leave my dirty shell\r\nbut there is a weird sound makes me to hide\r\n\r\n\r\nThey’re coming\r\nListen\r\nOh, they’re arriving\r\n\r\nand…\r\n\r\nThey draw me out\r\nInto black clouds\r\nThey bark and shout\r\n“You should not go out! You should not go out!”\r\nInjecting something cold in my brain\r\nMy brain is passing heat to my frame\r\nThe frame is lessening into string\r\nThe string is lessening into…\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nNo lights at all\r\nNo sounds at all\r\nNo scents at all\r\nAnd where is my jaw, and where is my jaw?\r\nMy lung is breathing inside others\r\nMy heart is bumping blood for all the fuckers\r\nMy brain is sinking with the leaders\r\nIt’s lucky that my bones are still here\r\n\r\nMy brain will always make you cry out loud\r\nNo dictators! No dictators!\r\nMy brain will always make you cry out loud\r\nFight for it! Keep going on!', '', 281, '', 'Fad', 'Sky Smiler', 'Fad', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-19 11:06:04', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47761, 148203, 0, 1, 'As Great As Those Great Volkswagon Ads (Demo)', '', '2010-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'I was walking alone when it rained on me\r\nI was sleeping alone when the lightning frightened me\r\n\r\nIt seemed, that’d be\r\nAnd yes, it’d be\r\n\r\nI just could do nothing but I could still play happily\r\n\r\n\r\nOne day there were two big eyes staring at me\r\nAs in the boring workshop I was falling into sleep\r\n\r\nShe is, pretty\r\nI was, lucky\r\n\r\nWhen we teamed, just like great artwork with copies\r\nI think that it’s the chemistry\r\n\r\n\r\nNot always be fine\r\nNot always be fine\r\nI know that we may both cry\r\n\r\nKeep trying to be fine\r\nKeep trying to be fine\r\nI’m willing to give both of us some time\r\n\r\n\r\nShe just, called me\r\nAnd she, was here\r\n\r\nWhen we team, just like great artwork with copies\r\nAnd then if we dream, there will be a creature that\r\nmay be stunning than those Volkswagen ads\r\n\r\n\r\nLet’s stand by each other\r\nStand by each other\r\nStand by each other forever\r\n\r\nLet’s grow plenty of flowers\r\nPlenty of flowers\r\nPlenty of flowers that will be held later', '', 195, '', 'Fad', 'Sky Smiler', 'Fad', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-19 11:08:06', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47762, 148203, 0, 1, 'Sleep Out (Demo)', '', '2010-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'He’s lying, lying and lying\r\nin the street I walk\r\nHe’s begging, begging and begging\r\nin the street I walk\r\nHe’s sleeping, sleeping and sleeping\r\nin the street I walk\r\nI’m thinking, thinking and thinking\r\nto give him money or not\r\n\r\nHe can try by himself\r\nHe can work by himself\r\nHe can earn by himself\r\nHe can live by himself\r\n\r\n\r\nShe’s kneeling, kneeling and kneeling\r\nin the street I walk\r\nShe’s begging, begging and begging\r\nin the street I walk\r\nShe’s crying, crying and crying\r\nin the street I walk\r\nI’m thinking, thinking and thinking\r\nto give her money or not\r\n\r\nShe can try by herself\r\nShe can work by herself\r\nShe can earn by herself\r\nShe can live by herself\r\n\r\n\r\nOh she has a baby\r\nOh she has a baby', '', 359, '', 'Fad', 'Sky Smiler', 'Fad', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-19 11:11:44', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47763, 148203, 0, 1, 'Dream in Dream (Demo)', '', '2011-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'Falling down\r\nfrom the snow-capped mountain\r\nand then my eyes open\r\nThere’re many dead people, floating on the ocean\r\nThe ocean’s calm\r\n\r\nI, should be on the way\r\nto the USA, looking for new days\r\nand I, had met a girl called Rose\r\nShe is now alive or gone?\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you have a dream, try your best staying in\r\nAs in this loveless cruel world, i feel like being trapped in limbo\r\nWe can’t beat the law, the law of gravity\r\nIt’s ok as we sometimes fall, to wake up and then stand up once more\r\n\r\n\r\nSky’s howling\r\nSoon I’m hit by the lightening\r\nand then my eyes open\r\nthat’s the hard-core song, for morning call\r\nI’m late\r\n\r\nI, should be on the way\r\nto the working place, repeating the days\r\nbut I, used to draw and paint\r\nnow the pictures are fading away', '', 209, '', 'Fad', 'Sky Smiler', 'Fad', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-19 11:13:14', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47764, 148203, 0, 1, 'Salamander (Demo)', '', '2011-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'Thom got paralyzed left eye when he’s a child\r\nWith the nickname that was called salamander\r\nThe first time when we’re talking in mobile\r\nYou said you like adopting little salamanders\r\n\r\nThom got drunk in a pub near his home\r\nHe tried to get attention of a woman\r\nWe had meal in a place near your home\r\nYou said I was a wise and mature man\r\n\r\nYou said you are a creep\r\nAnd you don’t belong here\r\nAll the melodies stayed along with me tonight\r\nAnd what the hell am I doing here?\r\nI don’t know to make you happy\r\nSo I just also think that I don’t belong here\r\n\r\n\r\nThom made records and sang like an angel\r\nAnd broke down in tears inside the studio\r\nI tried to play guitar and sang solo\r\nYou said the way I sang was beautiful\r\n\r\nNo alarms\r\nNo alarms\r\nAnd also no surprises\r\nYou got drunk and got the guts\r\nYour answer was already not a surprise\r\n\r\nMany fake plastic trees\r\nWere embedded in here\r\nAnd the melodies stayed along with me tonight\r\nI don’t know baby what I can do\r\nI have to admit that I lose\r\nSo I wish I could be the one you tend to choose\r\n\r\nStay along with me tonight\r\nI don’t know baby what I can do\r\nI have to admit that I lose\r\nSo I wish I could be the one you tend to choose\r\n\r\nNo alarms\r\nNo alarms\r\nAnd also no surprises', '', 296, '', 'Fad', 'Sky Smiler', 'Fad', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-19 11:16:17', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47765, 148203, 0, 1, 'So Tired (Demo)', '', '2011-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'I’m so tired\r\nI’m so tired\r\nI’m so tired\r\nI’m so tired of you, of you\r\n\r\nI’m so tired\r\nI’m so tired\r\nI’m so tired\r\nThe words you always made\r\n\r\nDamn busy\r\nYou’re so busy\r\nYou told me you got no time for the practice\r\nSo active\r\nYou’re so active when you’re buying Gucci\r\n\r\nYou said you will go to Disneyland with girlfriend in weekend\r\nAnd take a lot of the pictures with new Canon Digital Cam.\r\nYou said you just kept fucking stocks and got nothing to pay rent\r\nBut one day somehow you have just bought the tix to Japan\r\n\r\nI can’t meddle\r\nbut I hope you’ll know\r\nNot everyone can keep everythings in control\r\nYou will get nothing bold when you get old\r\nDon’t you know time does always flow\r\n\r\n1 2 3 4 5 6 7 and start over\r\n\r\nHow many days still can we live for?\r\n\r\nSo busy\r\nYou’re so busy\r\nYou told me you got no time to see movie\r\nSo active\r\nYou’re so active when you go to the parties\r\n\r\nEverytime when i send you message on the far way to home\r\nFeels like dropping a stone into bottomless black hole\r\nEverytime when i call you and you’re teasing with other people\r\n\r\nWu Oh Wu Oh\r\n\r\nYou don’t want to be friend with me da da da', '', 272, '', 'Fad', 'Sky Smiler', 'Fad', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-05-19 11:19:15', '2015-03-12 13:52:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
